        <h2>Empathy and Respect</h2>
        <p>
        We are considerate, inclusive empathetic and respectful in all aspects.
        </p>
        <h2>Quality</h2>
        <p>
        We always do the best job possible given the situation and constraints at hand.
        </p>
        <h2>Professionalism</h2>
        <p>
        We always behave in a manner that represents us as professionals.
        </p>
        <h2>Honesty</h2>
        <p>
        We have the courage to be honest, even when it's hard, and transparent even if that seems scary.
        </p>
        <h2>Collaboration and Shared Ownership</h2>
        <p>
        We work together, communicate clearly and solve problems as a team.
        </p>
        <h2>Simplicity</h2>
        <p>
